snippet.title: Title_Pending - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1288900/Title_Pending/

Title_Pending will be releasing September 27th, 2022! 

Become a playtester and explore Matthew Stanton's work in progress video game to unravel the mystery behind JMC Gaming Enterprises...

Join our Discord: https://devbeef.com/discord
Follow us on Twitter: https://devbeef.com/twitter
